  <sect1 remap="h1">
    <title>Jajuk 1.3 - New and Noteworthy</title>
    <para>
Jajuk team is pleased to present this new major upgrade that intend
to reply to users most urgent requests: new audio formats support,
sound breaks and memory footprint reduction. This release
brings as well major GUI improvements and many new features. </para>
    <sect2 remap="h2">
      <title>Sound engine</title>
      <para>
        <informaltable frame="none">
          <tgroup cols="2">
            <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="50*"/>
            <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="50*"/>
            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry><para>New
Audio formats supported</para></entry>
                <entry><para>Support for Flac, WMA, Real Player
Audio has been added (requires mplayer 1.0pre8 or later under Linux
and Mac). See current formats <ulink url="./jajuk-hs/default/html/formats.xml">support list</ulink>.</para>                  <para>
                    <informalfigure>
                      <mediaobject>
                        <imageobject>
                          <imagedata fileref="./images/new_formats.jpg" format="JPG"/>                        </imageobject>
                      </mediaobject>
                    </informalfigure>
</para>
</entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </informaltable>
</para>
      <para>
        <informaltable frame="none">
          <tgroup cols="2">
            <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="50*"/>
            <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="50*"/>
            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry><para>Better
support for current formats</para></entry>
                <entry><para>o Better sound quality</para>                  <para>
 o Seeking inside tracks is much faster</para>
                  <para>
 o No more sound skippings</para>
                  <para>
 o Ogg seeking now available</para>
</entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </informaltable>
</para>
      <para>
        <informaltable frame="none">
          <tgroup cols="2">
            <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="50*"/>
            <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="50*"/>
            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry><para>Full queue now
remembered at next startup</para></entry>
                <entry><para>When using Start last track startup option,
full queue is now remembered at next Jajuk session and not only
last track</para></entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </informaltable>
</para>
    </sect2>
    <sect2 remap="h2">
      <title>Interface
      </title>
      <informaltable frame="none">
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="50*"/>
          <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="50*"/>
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry><para>New visual
identity</para></entry>
              <entry><para>Jajuk project has now an official
graphist that designed new icons, splashscreens and
website</para>                <para>
                  <informalfigure>
                    <mediaobject>
                      <imageobject>
                        <imagedata fileref="./images/jajuk-title.png" format="PNG"/>                      </imageobject>
                    </mediaobject>
                  </informalfigure>
</para>
</entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </informaltable>

      <informaltable frame="none">
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="50*"/>
          <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="50*"/>
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry><para>New
perspective selector</para></entry>
              <entry><para>
                  <informalfigure>
                    <mediaobject>
                      <imageobject>
                        <imagedata fileref="./images/perspective_selector.jpg" format="JPG"/>                      </imageobject>
                    </mediaobject>
                  </informalfigure>
Perspective
selector is bigger and adopted Firefox look and feel</para></entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </informaltable>

      <informaltable frame="none">
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="50*"/>
          <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="50*"/>
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry><para>
Hidable views </para></entry>
              <entry><para>
                  <informalfigure>
                    <mediaobject>
                      <imageobject>
                        <imagedata fileref="./images/dockable.jpg" format="JPG"/>                      </imageobject>
                    </mediaobject>
                  </informalfigure>
Hardly used views can now be
hided for space saving (it is the new default Playlists Repository
view)</para></entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </informaltable>
      <informaltable frame="none">
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="50*"/>
          <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="50*"/>
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry><para>
Dynamic toolbars</para></entry>
              <entry><para>
                  <informalfigure>
                    <mediaobject>
                      <imageobject>
                        <imagedata fileref="./images/toolbars.jpg" format="JPG"/>                      </imageobject>
                    </mediaobject>
                  </informalfigure>
Toolbars are now dynamic and can be moved
anywhere in the entire Jajuk frame (at the left / right / top or
bottom). Their new positions are saved between jajuk sessions.</para></entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </informaltable>

      <informaltable frame="none">
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="50*"/>
          <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="50*"/>
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry><para>
Hotkeys and Intellitype keyboard support(Windows only)</para></entry>
              <entry><para>
                  <itemizedlist>
                    <listitem>
                      <para> Jajuk keystrokes now works from the entire desktop and not only
when Jajuk get focus (hotkey)</para>
                    </listitem>
                    <listitem>
                      <para> Jajuk main media functions now works from Microsoft Intellitype
keyboads</para>
                    </listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</para></entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </informaltable>

    </sect2>
    <sect2 remap="h2">
      <title>New features
      </title>
      <informaltable frame="none">
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="50*"/>
          <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="50*"/>
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry><para>Reporting</para></entry>
              <entry><para>Jajuk now provides a collection
reporter giving the ability to produce an HTML or XML collection
report. It can be applied on the entire collection or from lower
levels (artists, device...)</para>                <para>
                  <informalfigure>
                    <mediaobject>
                      <imageobject>
                        <imagedata fileref="./images/report.jpg" format="JPG"/>                      </imageobject>
                    </mediaobject>
                  </informalfigure>
</para>
</entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </informaltable>

      <informaltable frame="none">
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="50*"/>
          <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="50*"/>
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry><para>New
Track-by-track or Album-by-album global shuffle modes</para></entry>
              <entry><para>
                  <informalfigure>
                    <mediaobject>
                      <imageobject>
                        <imagedata fileref="./images/shuffle_modes.jpg" format="JPG"/>                      </imageobject>
                    </mediaobject>
                  </informalfigure>
It is now possible
to fine tune Global shuffle and Novelties functions by
selecting track by track (current default) or album by album mode
(full albums are played)</para></entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </informaltable>

      <informaltable frame="none">
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="50*"/>
          <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="50*"/>
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry><para>Animation
view pattern</para></entry>
              <entry><para>Animation View text is now
 customizable using a pattern</para>                <para>
                  <informalfigure>
                    <mediaobject>
                      <imageobject>
                        <imagedata fileref="./images/animation_pattern.jpg" format="JPG"/>                      </imageobject>
                    </mediaobject>
                  </informalfigure>
 </para>
</entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </informaltable>

      <informaltable frame="none">
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="50*"/>
          <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="50*"/>
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry><para>Ambience
selector</para></entry>
              <entry><para>It is now possible to filter
selection from global functions (Novelties, Shuffle, Best-of) with
selected ambience from the combo box at their left.
                  <informalfigure>
                    <mediaobject>
                      <imageobject>
                        <imagedata fileref="./images/ambience_selector.jpg" format="JPG"/>                      </imageobject>
                    </mediaobject>
                  </informalfigure>
</para></entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </informaltable>

      <informaltable frame="none">
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="50*"/>
          <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="50*"/>
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry><para>Catalog
view enhancements</para></entry>
              <entry><para>
                  <itemizedlist>
                    <listitem>
                      <para> Catalog View now displays each cover only once (even if several
albums have the same cover)</para>
                    </listitem>
                    <listitem>
                      <para> The number of displayed covers are now limited and a pagination
sysem is now available.</para>
                    </listitem>
</itemizedlist>
                  <informalfigure>
                    <mediaobject>
                      <imageobject>
                        <imagedata fileref="./images/page_selector.jpg" format="JPG"/>                      </imageobject>
                    </mediaobject>
                  </informalfigure>
</para></entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </informaltable>

      <informaltable frame="none">
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="50*"/>
          <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="50*"/>
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry><para>New
Configuration menu</para></entry>
              <entry><para>
                  <informalfigure>
                    <mediaobject>
                      <imageobject>
                        <imagedata fileref="./images/configuration_menu.jpg" format="JPG"/>                      </imageobject>
                    </mediaobject>
                  </informalfigure>
A new Configuration menu now agregates
all the option and confguration wizards</para></entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </informaltable>

      <informaltable frame="none">
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="50*"/>
          <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="50*"/>
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry><para>New
Debug dialog</para></entry>
              <entry><para>
                  <informalfigure>
                    <mediaobject>
                      <imageobject>
                        <imagedata fileref="./images/debug_dialog.jpg" format="JPG"/>                      </imageobject>
                    </mediaobject>
                  </informalfigure>
A new <emphasis>Show
debug traces </emphasis> feature available from the Help menu
displays current traces.</para></entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </informaltable>

      <informaltable frame="none">
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="50*"/>
          <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="50*"/>
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry><para>Wikipedia
view under Linux</para></entry>
              <entry><para>
                  <informalfigure>
                    <mediaobject>
                      <imageobject>
                        <imagedata fileref="./images/wikipedia_linux.jpg" format="JPG"/>                      </imageobject>
                    </mediaobject>
                  </informalfigure>
</para>                <para>
 Wikipedia view is now available under Linux</para>
</entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </informaltable>

      <para>Detailed changes can be found in this <ulink url="http://jajuk.sourceforge.net/changes-report.xml">changelog
report</ulink></para>
    </sect2>
  </sect1>
